reviewText: If you haven't seen this series it's a must. It's great and funny.

Written by Muslims for the rest of us.  And while US television is too chicken to air it, Canadians and those of us with access to CBC TV enjoyed the everyday ups and downs that all of us experience, with a Muslim twist.  If you can, get your hands on the first show from the first season.  Going through airport security will surely make you laugh.

I hope someday a US network will have the guts to air this series without censuring it.
